					<p>Modified Tupperware containers! Awesome! üòÄ</p>
<p>This piece is mostly a description of how our bodies, even down to the air we breathe, have become commodities. It begins and ends with our protagonist, who appears to be either about to sell, or purchase something.</p>
<p>I enjoyed the humour in this, and how it sneaks up on you. Along with the Tupperware, I also enjoyed the &#8220;renting space&#8221; comparison.</p>
